00:13:41.330 --> 00:13:44.330
Well in the end, I'll just end with a story.

00:13:44.330 --> 00:13:46.330
This is called "The Captain's Hat Story."

00:13:46.330 --> 00:13:48.330
The captain was a captain of a sea-going ship.

00:13:48.330 --> 00:13:50.330
It goes very slowly.

00:13:50.330 --> 00:13:52.330
And there were lots of passengers on the ship,

00:13:52.330 --> 00:13:54.330
and they were getting bored, so the captain invited them on the deck.

00:13:54.330 --> 00:13:56.330
"Wear all your colorful clothes and sing and dance,

00:13:56.330 --> 00:13:58.330
and I'll provide you with good food and drinks."

00:13:58.330 --> 00:14:00.330
And the captain would wear a cap everyday

00:14:00.330 --> 00:14:02.330
and join in the regalia.

00:14:02.330 --> 00:14:04.330
The first day, it was a huge umbrella cap,

00:14:04.330 --> 00:14:06.330
like a captain's cap.

00:14:06.330 --> 00:14:09.330
That night, when the passengers would be sleeping,

00:14:09.330 --> 00:14:11.330
he would give it one more fold,

00:14:11.330 --> 00:14:13.330
and the second day, he would be wearing a fireman's cap --

00:14:13.330 --> 00:14:15.330
with a little shoot just like a designer cap,

00:14:15.330 --> 00:14:18.330
because it protects the spinal cord.

00:14:18.330 --> 00:14:20.330
And the second night, he would take the same cap

00:14:20.330 --> 00:14:22.330
and give it another fold.

00:14:22.330 --> 00:14:24.330
And the third day, it would be a Shikari cap --

00:14:24.330 --> 00:14:27.330
just like an adventurer's cap.

00:14:27.330 --> 00:14:30.330
And the third night, he would give it two more folds --

00:14:30.330 --> 00:14:32.330
and this is a very, very famous cap.

00:14:32.330 --> 00:14:34.330
If you've seen any of our Bollywood films,

00:14:34.330 --> 00:14:36.330
this is what the policeman wears,

00:14:36.330 --> 00:14:38.330
it's called a zapalu cap.

00:14:38.330 --> 00:14:41.330
It's been catapulted to international glory.

00:14:41.330 --> 00:14:44.330
And we must not forget that he was the captain of the ship.

00:14:44.330 --> 00:14:46.330
So that's a ship.

00:14:46.330 --> 00:14:48.330
And now the end:

00:14:48.330 --> 00:14:50.330
everyone was enjoying the journey very much.

00:14:50.330 --> 00:14:52.330
They were singing and dancing.

00:14:52.330 --> 00:14:55.330
Suddenly there was a storm and huge waves.

00:14:55.330 --> 00:14:58.330
And all the ship can do is to dance and pitch along with the waves.

00:14:58.330 --> 00:15:00.330
A huge wave comes and slaps the front

00:15:00.330 --> 00:15:02.330
and knocks it down.

00:15:02.330 --> 00:15:05.330
And another one comes and slaps the aft and knocks it down.

00:15:05.330 --> 00:15:07.330
And there's a third one over here.

00:15:07.330 --> 00:15:09.330
This swallows the bridge and knocks it down.

00:15:09.330 --> 00:15:11.330
And the ship sinks,

00:15:11.330 --> 00:15:13.330
and the captain has lost everything,

00:15:13.330 --> 00:15:16.330
but for a life jacket.

00:15:16.330 --> 00:15:18.330
Thank you so much.

00:15:18.330 --> 00:15:24.330
(Applause)

